# API Documentation

# Group Users

## Register a New User [POST /api/users/register]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + name: John Doe (string) - The name of the user
        + email: john@example.com (string) - The email of the user
        + password: password123 (string) - The password of the user
        + apartment: 101 (string) - The apartment of the user

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + message: User registered successfully (string)
        + user (object)
            + id: 1 (number) - The ID of the user
            + name: John Doe (string)
            + email: john@example.com (string)
            + apartment: 101 (string)

## Login a User [POST /api/users/login]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + email: john@example.com (string) - The email of the user
        + password: password123 (string) - The password of the user

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + token: fake-jwt-token (string) - The JWT token

## Get User Profile [GET /api/users/profile]
+ Request
    + Headers
        Authorization: Bearer {token}

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + user (object)
            + id: 1 (number) - The ID of the user
            + name: John Doe (string)
            + email: john@example.com (string)
            + apartment: 101 (string)

# Group Bookings

## Create a New Booking [POST /api/bookings]
+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
        Authorization: Bearer {token}
    + Attributes (object)
        + resourceId: resource-id (string) - The ID of the resource
        + startTime: 2023-10-01T10:00:00Z (string) - The start time of the booking
        + endTime: 2023-10-01T12:00:00Z (string) - The end time of the booking

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + message: Booking created successfully (string)
        + booking (object)
            + id: 1 (number) - The ID of the booking
            + resourceId: resource-id (string)
            + startTime: 2023-10-01T10:00:00Z (string)
            + endTime: 2023-10-01T12:00:00Z (string)

## Get All Bookings [GET /api/bookings]
+ Request
    + Headers
        Authorization: Bearer {token}

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[object])
        + id: 1 (number) - The ID of the booking
        + resourceId: resource-id (string)
        + startTime: 2023-10-01T10:00:00Z (string)
        + endTime: 2023-10-01T12:00:00Z (string)

## Get Bookings by User [GET /api/bookings/user/{userId}]
+ Request
    + Headers
        Authorization: Bearer {token}

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[object])
        + id: 1 (number) - The ID of the booking
        + resourceId: resource-id (string)
        + startTime: 2023-10-01T10:00:00Z (string)
        + endTime: 2023-10-01T12:00:00Z (string)
